g/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The process began with GK Elite conducting a survey asking athletes about their preferred colors, necklines, fabrics, crystal coverage, and other design elements, GK Elite lead designer Jeanne Diaz told Business Insider.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999054882709, \"rank\": 8.916598459455597e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999054882709, \"rank\": 8.916598459455597e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_of_Arc\", \"score\": 0.9998831286153801, \"rank\": 0.00011688479673676306, \"text\": \"Jeanne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_of_Arc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joan_of_Arc\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Business Insider\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_Insider\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sportswear company then collaborated with USA Gymnastics and a panel of former athletes to create the designs.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999824922, \"rank\": 1.7560984049262397e-11, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, the leotards were sewn at GK Elite's in-house manufacturing floor in Reading, Pennsylvania.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading,_Pennsylvania\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reading, Pennsylvania\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading,_Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading,_Pennsylvania\"}, {\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading,_Pennsylvania\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reading, Pennsylvania\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading,_Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading,_Pennsylvania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With custom fabrics and thousands of crystals, each leotard is valued at around $5,000, Diaz said.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic athletes themselves did not see any of the finalleotard designsuntil they were named to the team, a reveal that Diaz described as \\\"a really special moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the 2024 Olympics, the GK Elite design team took inspiration from the host city of Paris, incorporating French fashion elements and paying tribute to the City of Light.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999054882709, \"rank\": 8.916598459455597e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}, {\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999906777, \"rank\": 9.374766709153296e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9913298178036652, \"rank\": 0.007322077029287133, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The leotards are still unmistakably American with nods to Fourth of July fireworks and the \\\"Star-Spangled Banner\\\" in red, white, and blue.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Under the arena lights, some of that detail might get lost, but that's OK because the detail is also for the athletes to feel confident, and that confidence will hopefully translate to their performances,\\\" Diaz said.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are hidden details you may have missed in Team USA's leotard designs.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1693, \"end\": 1701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.99590811068104, \"rank\": 0.003952101822166581, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA wore the \\\"Sovereign Sparkle\\\" leotards to podium training on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.99590811068104, \"rank\": 0.003952101822166581, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The firework-inspired design adds an \\\"Americana element\\\" to the leotard collection, Diaz said.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sparkles on the leotard also evoke the Eiffel Tower when it lights up at night.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA wore the \\\"Star Spangled Shine\\\" designs to the qualification event on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.99590811068104, \"rank\": 0.003952101822166581, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The red, white, and blue crystals reference the American flag, while the gold crystals pay tribute to the team's historic gold-medal wins.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.090824725224392e-19, \"text\": \"American flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diaz said that the criss-cross crystal pattern was inspired by the \\\"boning-style lines\\\" of corsetry.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GK Elite said the velvet pieces, which are also adorned with colorful crystals, add \\\"a touch of sophistication and comfort\\\" to the design.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999054882709, \"rank\": 8.916598459455597e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The star pattern is featured on the leotard's upper bodice and sleeves.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Diaz said that Olympic athletes often prefer mesh sleeves since they are more breathable.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 1996 US women's gymnastics team made history by winning the first US team gold in the women's all-around event, earning them the nickname \\\"Magnificent Seven.\\\"\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2625, \"end\": 2627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9776841477133128, \"rank\": 0.022739107533245075, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2686, \"end\": 2688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9776841477133128, \"rank\": 0.022739107533245075, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They were the pioneers,\\\" Diaz said of the 1996 team, adding that the throwback design helps the 2024 Olympians \\\"carry a piece of that legacy with them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The design is titled \\\"Go for Glory.\\\"\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic gymnastics leotardshave definitely evolved over time,\\\" Diaz said.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have gone from little to no crystal coverage at all, to now tens of thousands of Swarovski crystals adorning the Paris Olympic leotards.\\\"\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3165, \"end\": 3170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999906777, \"rank\": 9.374766709153296e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diaz added that this year's gymnasts asked for more crystal coverage in the GK Elite leotard design survey.\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3267, \"end\": 3269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999054882709, \"rank\": 8.916598459455597e-08, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We loved that answer,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jump to\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3342, \"entities\": []}]}"